00:07:30,020 --> 00:07:32,220
Well...

80
00:07:32,220 --> 00:07:36,600
In your childhood, were you the young savage's friend?

81
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:39,280
She didn't deserve me.

82
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:42,940
I went to Yueliang Mountain.

83
00:07:42,940 --> 00:07:45,160
She painted a lot in the cave.

84
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:48,460
About your mother having fun with you two.

85
00:07:48,460 --> 00:07:50,660
Yes.

86
00:07:50,660 --> 00:07:53,340
In case she was lonely,

87
00:07:53,340 --> 00:07:55,940
my mother took me up there to play with her.

88
00:07:57,840 --> 00:08:00,540
Why would a beast be lonely?

89
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:04,500
Did you never play with her there?

90
