I played with her happily and taught her to paint.

92
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,500
You taught her to paint?

93
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:14,540
Or who else did?

94
00:08:14,540 --> 00:08:19,040
If nobody had taught her, how could a beast learn to paint?

95
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:21,040
Stop calling her a beast.

96
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,580
Show some respect, will you?

97
00:08:22,580 --> 00:08:25,040
It's too early to be angry.

98
00:08:27,500 --> 00:08:32,760
When you know what happened later, you'll go mad.

99
00:08:33,700 --> 00:08:36,320
I played with her happily.

100
