And she wouldn't have obeyed me.

102
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,940
What did you do?

103
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:50,640
Nothing, actually.

104
00:08:52,060 --> 00:08:55,240
I just chewed a mushroom

105
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:58,220
