106
00:08:58,220 --> 00:09:00,100
I frothed at the mouth.

107
00:09:08,660 --> 00:09:12,160
You pretended to be poisoned, and she took you to the village.

108
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:14,860
In the village, I got better.

109
00:09:14,860 --> 00:09:17,460
 I shouted and shouted. 

110
