You should have seen how they hit her with stones.

112
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,930
 It's over there. 

113
00:09:24,930 --> 00:09:26,830
 There. 

114
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,720
Shut up!

115
00:09:41,160 --> 00:09:45,180
You know what? She deserved it.

116
00:09:45,180 --> 00:09:47,720
I used to have a happy family.

117
00:09:49,860 --> 00:09:52,000
 Because of her, 

118
00:09:52,980 --> 00:09:55,100
I lost everything.

119
00:09:55,100 --> 00:09:57,200
My mother abandoned me.

120
00:10:00,180 --> 00:10:02,820
My father got a new wife.

121
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:06,920
Do you know what a terrible life I had?

122
00:10:10,500 --> 00:10:13,280
It was all because of that beast.

123
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:17,540
She deserved it.

124
00:10:57,340 --> 00:10:59,180
Miss Lian.

125
00:11:00,300 --> 00:11:03,180
You never understood their love.

126
00:11:03,180 --> 00:11:06,120
You had a loving mother.

127
00:11:07,300 --> 00:11:12,820
You also had an honest and kind sister.

128
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:17,220
You lost both of them.

129
00:11:17,220 --> 00:11:19,640
But it's not that they abandoned you,

130
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:23,240
but you didn't deserve them.

131
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:25,640
All the time,

132
00:11:26,580 --> 00:11:28,380
you never deserved.

133
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:43,520
Well, you called her a beast.

134
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:45,620
But in my eyes,

135
00:11:47,260 --> 00:11:49,260
