136
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:32,100
How tragic! That girl was knocked away.

137
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:44,060
Such a miserable car accident.

138
00:12:44,060 --> 00:12:45,380
The police even came.

139
00:12:45,380 --> 00:12:47,660
Look at the tiny pieces of glass.

140
00:12:47,660 --> 00:12:49,700
- And the blood. 
 - Yes.

141
00:12:49,700 --> 00:12:53,140
How miserable! Can she survive?

142
00:12:53,140 --> 00:12:56,340
I heard it was a mass of blood. That's horrible.

143
