Mu Dai can stay here for a few more days for further observation.

173
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:46,260
Okay. I get it.

174
00:15:53,620 --> 00:15:55,380
Long time no see.

175
00:16:00,680 --> 00:16:03,140
Dr. He is an old friend of mine.

176
00:16:03,140 --> 00:16:05,400
Eight years ago, he worked at Huacheng People's Hospital

177
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:07,120
and dealt with Mu Dai's case.

